    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW 330i xDrive finished in Alpine White. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage when not in use. The exterior retains a deep, brilliant gloss, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor rock chips on the front hood and a small, superficial scuff on the lower rear bumper\u2014honest wear for a car that has been enjoyed on the road. Inside, the Black SensaTec upholstery is in great shape with no rips, tears, or fading; the cabin is smoke-free and retains its premium feel. All interior electronics, including the iDrive navigation system, sunroof, and dual-zone climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, this BMW is in great health. I have a complete folder of service records from the local dealership, including a recent oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection performed just 1,500 miles ago. The tires show healthy tread depth, and the 2.0L turbocharged engine delivers smooth, consistent power without any leaks or warning lights on the dash. This is a solid, well-cared-for vehicle that offers a perfect balance of performance and luxury.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
